## Performance Metrics

| Metric | FireCut | SPLICE |
|--------|---------|--------|
| **Package Size** | ~80MB+ (with node_modules) | 172KB (CEP) + 143KB (UXP) |
| **Installation Time** | 2-5 minutes (manual) | 30-60 seconds (automated) |
| **User Errors** | High (manual process) | Minimal (automated validation) |
| **Update Process** | Full reinstall | Automated update check |
| **Security Warnings** | Possible (unsigned) | None (signed + notarized) |
| **Support Burden** | High (manual steps) | Low (automated) |

