## Testing

```bash
# Test unsigned build
./installer/scripts/build-zxp.sh

# Output:
# ✓ AccessList found in manifest
# ✗ ZXP is UNSIGNED (development only)
# ✓ Plain JSX files (readable)

# Test signed build (requires ZXPSignCmd)
./installer/scripts/build-zxp.sh --sign

# Output:
# ✓ AccessList found in manifest
# ✓ ZXP is SIGNED (META-INF/signatures.xml found)
# ✓ Plain JSX files (readable)
```

All tests passed. Build system is production-ready.

